OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FWe're now halfway through the World Cup
OL,7,Fand a familiar complaint is emerging.
OL,9,FThis week's Newswatch included
OL,10,Fcomplaints about the scheduling and
OL,11,Fcontent of the main BBC One news
OL,12,Fbulletins.
OL,14,FSome viewers are unhappy that the news
OL,15,Fhas been at unusual times on busy news
OL,16,Fdays. Others expressed concern about
OL,17,Fsports stories dominating the
OL,18,Fbulletins.
OL,20,FIt's a shame that, on this occasion,
OL,21,Fnobody from BBC News was able to join a
OL,22,Fstudio discussion with the viewers.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14202
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FWhen it comes to scheduling I have a
OL,7,Flot of sympathy for the viewers who
OL,8,Fcomplained and a lot of sympathy for
OL,9,Fthe BBC's position.
OL,11,FFor as long as I can remember, the
OL,12,FWorld Cup and the Olympics have played
OL,13,Fhavoc with the schedule.
OL,15,FI recall occasions during the Falklands
OL,16,FConflict in 1982 when the Nine o'Clock
OL,17,FNews was delayed.
OL,19,FThe day of Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,20,Fresignation as Prime Minister provides
OL,21,Fa case in point.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14203
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FOn that day, BBC One was due to run its
OL,7,Fmain news programmes at 5pm and 9pm
OL,8,Fwith shorter durations than usual.
OL,10,FBoth were actually extended to
OL,11,Fappropriate lengths by starting them
OL,12,Fhalf an hour earlier than billed.
OL,14,FAny suggestion the PM's resignation did
OL,15,Fnot receive the depth of coverage it
OL,16,Fmerited are wide of the mark. It should
OL,17,Falso be remembered that BBC One stayed
OL,18,Fwith rolling news for most of the
OL,19,Fdaytime.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14204
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut what about the person who simply
OL,7,Flikes to sit down and watch the News at
OL,8,FSix or News at Ten out of habit?
OL,10,FThis becomes a more nuanced discussion.
OL,12,FHere's where I stand.
OL,14,FFirstly, the BBC's live World Cup games
OL,15,Fshould be shown on BBC One as far as
OL,16,Fpossible. To suggest they should be
OL,17,Froutinely shown on Two ` far less a
OL,18,Fdigital channel or the red button `
OL,19,Fimplies a failure to appreciate just
OL,20,Fhow popular the World Cup is.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14205
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FSecondly, the main BBC News bulletins
OL,7,Falso belong on BBC One. They are the
OL,8,Fspine of the channel.
OL,10,FA news bulletin displaced by the World
OL,11,FCup on BBC One will probably still get
OL,12,Fmore viewers than a bulletin shown at
OL,13,Fthe normal time but shifted to Two.
OL,15,FThere are other problems too.
OL,17,FIf the network news was moved to Two,
OL,18,Fit would have to be divorced from the
OL,19,Fregional news. The English regions and
OL,20,FScotland cannot opt on Two.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14206
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FBefore digital switchover, there were
OL,7,Foccasions when the 6pm News Hour would
OL,8,Fswitch to Two at short notice during
OL,9,FWimbledon.
OL,11,FBut even if you support the BBC's
OL,12,Foverall situation, was there a case for
OL,13,Fripping up the schedule on the day of
OL,14,FStarmer's resignation to keep the news
OL,15,Fon BBC One at the normal times?
OL,17,FI'm sure this discussion would have
OL,18,Ftaken place.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14207
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe various dilemmas demonstrate the
OL,7,Fdifficulties and genuine contradictions
OL,8,Fwhich come from running a reactive
OL,9,Fchannel which is at the centre of
OL,10,Fnational life.
OL,12,FIncidentally, as far as I am aware
OL,13,Fthere have still been two main news
OL,14,Fprogrammes on One each weekday during
OL,15,Fthe World Cup ` even if they have
OL,16,Fsometimes been at unusual times.
OL,18,FITV 1 has ditched one of its news
OL,19,Fprogrammes completely on a number of
OL,20,Foccasions.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14208
SC,0008
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCScheduling and sport content on
OL,4,CBBC One news programmes
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn general, the News at Six and News at
OL,7,FTen should be firmly anchored. I have
OL,8,Fexpressed concern before when the times
OL,9,Fhave slipped because of The Traitors or
OL,10,Fthe final of The Apprentice.
OL,12,FBut major sports events where the
OL,13,Ftimings are outside the BBC's control
OL,14,Fare the exception to this rule.
OL,16,FIt's annoying for people who don't
OL,17,Fenjoy sport and they have my sympathy.
OL,18,FBut it's for the greater good.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100@
